test_shared_lib/

    @info Testing the use of the pathfinding library as a dynamic
    	  (shared) library.

    @warning Required: the library must exists => execute 'make shlib'
	     on the source code (i.e. cd ../.. && make shlib).



test_static_lib/

    @info Testing the use of the pathfinding library as an static library.

    @warning Required: the library must exists => execute 'make
	     staticlib' on the source code (i.e. cd ../.. && make
	     staticlib).



test_generating_lib/

    @info First, generates the library if necessary, then uses it as an
    	  static library.

